title: Jimmy Fallon + Conan 2015.06.15 (2-pack) Jeff.Garlin.x265.mkv
description:
This is x265 Not x264
Works great with the newer versions of VLC and potplayer
Or your own software media player with updated codecs
You also need to have at least a dual core cpu

I tried it on VLC version 2.2.1, potplayer version 1.6.54266
and MPC-HC version 1.7.9. If you want to update your VLC (When you have VLC running) at the top click HELP. Then click CHECK FOR UPDATES. Then it should walk you through the update.

-------------------------------------------

Late night talk show pack. Two shows from 2015.06.15

The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon 
With Aziz Ansari, Taylor Schilling, Adam Lambert
.
Conan
With Jeff Garlin, Angie Harmon, Tim Minchin
Team Conan battles Team Silicon Valley in the latest Halo
